MTD	mzTab-version	2.0.0-M
MTD	mzTab-ID	PLASMA_METABOLOMICS_XCMS_001
MTD	title	Plasma Metabolomics Study: Treated vs Untreated (XCMS 3.18)
MTD	description	Untargeted LC-MS metabolomics of human blood plasma comparing treated and untreated groups. Data was acquired in both positive and negative ionization mode (8 files each, 16 total). Peak picking and feature alignment performed with XCMS 3.18 in R. Metabolites identified against the Human Metabolome Database (HMDB).
